Your e-score represents your overall aging report. The key to healthy Aging is controlling "silent inﬂammation" or
Cardiometabolic disease-your e-score represents primarily your CardioMetabolic Risk Score (CRS) responsible for 80% of all
deaths worldwide.
Inﬂammation control: we will detect any disturbance of your endothelium
that may be "silently" eroding your health.
Nutrition: our physicians will measure your bodyfat and any metabolic
dysregulation.
Toxin Reduction: we will ﬁnd any toxins that maybe contributing to cellular,
nutritional, enzyme or hormonal imbalances.
Exercise: we measure your ﬁtness level as this will allow us to individualize
your exercise program so you can perform efectively and efciently in all
aspects of your life.
Genetics and aesthetics: Eternity uses the most advanced genetic and
telomere testing that measures cellular aging. (We can also assess how your
skin is aging.)
Restoration of hormones: hormones ar
e the juice of life. We measure your
hormonal levels and aim to restore them to the levels of a healthy 30 year old.
Advanced supplementation: we measure your vitamin, mineral, amino acids,
fatty acids, enzymes and intestinal ecology and replace targeted and core
nutraceuticals.
Lifelong (mind-body) learning: using CNS-VS and heart rate variability (HRV),
we assess your mindbody interaction to balance your central and autonomic
nervous system.
